    "body": "This PR implements the [dual-chunk flash attention](https://arxiv.org/pdf/2402.17463.pdf), a training-free method to extend model context length (see also #6139), with sparse attention (https://github.com/microsoft/MInference) support.\n\nThis PR requires the [sparse attention kernel](https://github.com/vllm-project/flash-attention/pull/33) from vllm-flash-attention. Qwen models with 1m context length support will be open-sourced in the next one or two weeks, and unit tests will be added later.\n\nFIX #12452\n\n",
    "created_at": "2025-01-08T13:09:11Z",
